These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, ebony
There 2 different types of food: corn, asparagus
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, classical
1. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the fan of classical##1
3. the person eating corn is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Color       | ebony       | emerald |
| Food         | asparagus | corn  |
| Beverage       | fanta    | 7up    |
| Music-Genre   | classical       | ambient      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bongani
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, british
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, orchid
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, bike
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the argentine is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Cigar      | bongani     | davidoff |
| Nationality           | argentine | british      |
| Flower   | orchid  | marigold      |
| Transport         | quad-bike | bike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
City: hamburg, colone
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, blue
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who likes blue##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| City      | hamburg | colone  |
| Game          | mah-jongg    | backgammon   |
| Pet   | hedgehog  | rabbit   |
| Color     | blue     | lavender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, august
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, sudoku
City: boston, new-york
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Birthday      | may       | august |
| Hobby          | sudoku         | camping    |
| City           | new-york | boston    |
| Sport   | tennis           | ice-hockey   |

