.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, jazz
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, december
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, australian
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the thai is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Music-Genre           | jazz | electronic     |
| Birthday   | january          | december |
| Nationality           | thai          | australian    |
| Hobby     | board-games            | filmmaking       |

 